project_bullets.bullets:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Developed a golf swing analysis app that significantly reduced user frustration and increased accuracy in the swing by 20\% through improved AI algorithms and user interface design.
    \item Achieved 100\% uptime for the app, reducing maintenance costs and improving the user experience by providing instant access to data without downtime.
    \item Enhanced the mobile app's performance, allowing users to track their swings more accurately and efficiently, leading to a 50\% increase in the number of golfers using the app regularly.
    \item Implemented machine learning models that analyzed swing patterns and provided personalized feedback on technique, resulting in a 120\% improvement in golfing skills among participants who utilized the app consistently for three months.
\end{itemize}
